Subject: [PATCH] PCI: keystone: Add link up check to ks_pcie_other_map_bus()
Mime-version: 1.0
Content-type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-transfer-encoding: 8bit
Git-commit: 9e9ec8d8692a6f64d81ef67d4fb6255af6be684b
